## Systemic Review Issue — Infra Follow-up

**Pattern azonosítva:**
| Occurrence | Date | Issue |
|---|---|---|
| #1-2 | 2026-06-24 | MSG-047, MSG-070 — Architect timeout + Librarian truncation |
| #3 | 2026-06-29 | MSG-076 — Architect REJECT (no feedback) + Librarian timeout |

**Root cause:** Technical issue a review process-ben:
- Architect session timeout / MCP communication issue
- Librarian output truncation

**Infra task:** Review process monitoring + retry logic (TODO for Infra terminal)

**Conductor policy:** Ha 1 reviewer APPROVE + 1 reviewer technical error (timeout) → **manual approve** amennyiben az implementáció tesztelt és működik.

